\pard\fs24\lang2057\f1\fs27\cf1\b\ltrpar\ql\sb450\sa45\li150\ri45 Q1.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb0\sa0\li567\ri567 Both the Caesar and Vernam ciphers are symmetric ciphers, whereas a public and private key encryption system is an asymmetric cipher system.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567 Explain the difference between a symmetric and an asymmetric cipher system\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li567\ri567 _______________________________________________________________________\par
