\f1\fs27\cf1\ltrpar\ql\sb450\sa45\li150\ri45 Q4.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb0\sa0\li567\ri567 To access an exam paper on the AQA website a student\u8217?s computer might need to make use of a Domain Name System (DNS) query which is transmitted to a DNS server.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (a)\~\~\~\~\~What is the purpose of a DNS server?\par
