\f1\fs27\cf1\ltrpar\ql\sb450\sa45\li150\ri45 Q5.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\b0\ltrpar\ql\sb0\sa0\li567\ri567 A message is to be transmitted from Computer A to Computer B. For security reasons, the message will be encrypted.\par
\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb240\sa0\li1134\ri567\fi-567 (a)\~\~\~\~\~What is encryption?\par
